headline: What BXP (BXP)'s Profit Rebound, Portfolio Sales and 2026 EPS Guidance Mean For Shareholders
summary: BXP, Inc. recently reported its fourth-quarter and full-year 2025 results, showing higher sales and revenue and a move to net income of US$248.49 million for the quarter and US$276.8 million for the year, alongside new 2026 EPS guidance of US$0.32–US$0.34 for the first quarter and US$2.08–US$2.29 for the full year.
